      <title>登记选民的团体感到受到新州法律的围困</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/05/16/1251289736/voter-registration-drive-state-restrictions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几个州共和党支持的新法律对选民登记工作中的小错误增加了巨额罚款或刑事处罚。随着团体的退出，他们接触到的选民也越来越少。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/2024/05/16/1251289736/voter-registration-drive-state-restrictions</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 09:01:06 GMT</pubDate>
