      <title>驳船撞上连接加尔维斯顿和鹈鹕岛的桥梁，导致石油泄漏</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/05/16/1251748089/barge-bridge-galveston-pelican-island</link>
      <description><![CDATA[碰撞的冲击力使连接加尔维斯顿和鹈鹕岛的桥梁碎片滚落在驳船上，并关闭了一段水道，以便工作人员清理泄漏物。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/2024/05/16/1251748089/barge-bridge-galveston-pelican-island</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 05:53:06 GMT</pubDate>
